Shukla would soon follow 16 balls and 20 runs later attempting to up the run rate only to find Patel in the deep to put paid to hopes of overhauling Kanbis’s total. 

Odhiambo returned with the ball to account for late order batsmen Abbas (10), Irfan Ellahi (16) and Singh (0) to further curtail the chase. 

Sir Ali finally folded for 133 for the loss of 9 wickets in their 20 overs. Wambua was last seen on Friday morning when her husband dropped her at work. President Magufuli has not appeared in public for over two weeks now. Police say they are monitoring the condition of the children before settling on the proper charge.